quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  7,156,"Winndanaa men ka aduna Й—oo moЖҙЖҙere, e ka laakara. Menen men tuubanii Ma. O Daali : \"Lepte Am Й—en, Mi meminay Й—e on mo Mi muuyi. Yurmeende Am nden yaajanii kala huunde. Arma Mi winndana nde Й“en hulooЙ“e (Alla), Й“e totta zakka, e Й“en gomЙ—inooЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  7,157,"ЖҒen jokkayЙ“e NulaaЙ—o on, Annabaajo humammbinneejo, on mo Й“e tawta fii mun no winndaa ka maЙ“Й“e ka Tawreeta e ka Linnjiila. Himo yamira Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, o haЙ—a Й“e ЕӢiГұere, himo daginana Й“e dagiiЙ—i Й—in, o harminana Й“e soЙ“uЙ—i Й—in, o ittana Й“e teddeelo e kolommbooje=tonngi wonunooЙ—e e hoore-maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e mo, Й“e teddini mo, Й“e walli mo, Й“e jokki annoora JippinaaЙ—o wonndude e makko ; Й“en, ko kamЙ“e woni malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  7,158,"Maaku : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, min ko mi NulaaЙ—o Alla e mooЙ—on on denndaangal, On Mo woodani Й—um laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa kanko. Himo wuurna wara. GomЙ—inee Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko Annabaajo humammbinneejo on, on gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla e KonnguЙ—i Makko Й—in. Jokkee mo, belajo'o, on feeway"
  7,159,"Hino e yimЙ“e Muusaa Й“en, mofte fewnirayЙ—e (yimЙ“e Й“en) e goonga, ko Й—um woni ko Й“e nunЙ—irta"
  7,160,"Men senndi Й“e gori sappo e Й—iЙ—i mofte. Men wahyini e Muusaa tuma nde yimЙ“e makko Й“en Й—aЙ“Й“irnoo mo yarnineede wonnde : \"Piyir tuggordu maa ndun hayre nden\". ЖҒulli sappo e Й—iЙ—i yallti e mayre. GomЙ—ii gorol kala andii yariride mu'un. Men Й—owdinirani Й“e duule, Men Jippini e maЙ“Й“e demmbe-njuuri, e teewu colli. \"Г‘aamee e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—i Men arsiki on\". ЖҒe tooГұaali Men, kono ko wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й“e tooГұaynoo"
  7,161,"Tuma nde Й“e wi'anaa : \"HoЙ—ee e ndee saare, Гұaamon e mayre nokku kala ka yiЙ—uЙ—on, wi'on : Й“oran men [goopi amen], naatiron ka damal ko on sujjuЙ“e, Men haforanay on goopi mon. Arma Men Й“eydana moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en"
  7,162,"TooГұuЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e wayliri konngol ngol ko wanaa ngol ngol Й“e wi'ananoo. Min Jippini e maЙ“Й“e lepte immorde ka kammu, sabu ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e tooГұa"
  7,163,"Lanndo Й“e fii saare wonunoonde nden ka sera maayo, tuma nde Й“e jaggitaynoo e Aseweere nden, tuma nde liЖҙЖҙi maЙ“Й“e Й—in araynooЙ“e Гұalnde Aseweere maЙ“Й“e nden ko Й—i hummbuЙ—i, Гұalnde woni wanaa aseweere maЙ“Й“e Й—i arataa Й“e. Ko wano nii Men jarriborta Й“e kon ko Й“e faasonqinoraynoo"
  7,164,"Tuma nde jamaa jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e wi'unoo : \"Ko honЙ—um waajoantoЙ—on yimЙ“e, Allaahu ko halkoowo Й“e maa O lepta Й“e lepte sattuЙ—e?\" ЖҒe wi'i : \"Ko [ittugol] nganto faade ka Joomi mo'on ; e belajo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e rentoto"
  7,165,"Nde Й“e yejjitunoo ko Й“e waajanoo fii mun kon, Men daЙ—ndi Й“en haЙ—aynooЙ“e e bone on, Men nanngiri Й“en tooГұuЙ“e lepte sattuЙ—e sabu ko Й“e faasonqinoraynoo"
  7,166,"Nde Й“e townitaninoo e ko Й“e haЙ—aa e mun kon, Men wi'ani Й“e : \"Laatee baaЙ—i jaasuЙ—i"
  7,167,"Janto tuma nde Joomi maa anndinnoo (wonnde) ma O Nulu e maЙ“Й“e haa Г‘alnde Darngal on meeЙ—inoowo Й“e lepte bonЙ—e. Pellet, Joomi maa ko yaawuЙ—e lepte, pellet kadi, ko O haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  7,168,"Men senndiri Й“e ka leydi jamaaji : hino e maЙ“Й“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e, hino e maЙ“Й“e ko jaasi Й—um. Men jarribori Й“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i e bonЙ—i, belajo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e ruttoto"
  7,169,"Lontii Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e lontii Й“e (bomЙ“e), Й“e roni Deftere nden, hiЙ“e Жҙetta weeЙ“itanЙ—e oo aduna Й“e wi'a : \"Aray men haforanee\". Si weeЙ“itannde sugu mun arii e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Жҙetta Й—um. Hara ahadi Deftere nden Жҙettidaaka e maЙ“Й“e, wonnde wata Й“e wowlu e Alla si wanaa goonga?! ЖҒe janngi ko woni e mayre. Ko galle laakara Й—en Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde Й“en rentiiЙ“e. E on haqqiltaa"
  7,170,"ЖҒen jogitotooЙ“e Deftere nden Й“e Гұinna julde, pellet, Menen Men yeebataa njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"